//**forreach loops**//


The foreach loop in C# isa block of code on each element in an array or a collection of items. When executing foreach loop it will transpose items in a collection or an array . 

Example:


  }
  string[] drinks = { "Coke", "Pepsi", "Rootbeer"};
  foreach (string day in drinks)
